➜珍稀甲虫格彩臂金龟现四川 它们在给人类警示？
http://www.sohu.com/a/424223350_114731	614
<p>原标题：它们频频出现却是给人类的警示 </p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201013/c6abcf9dd77347fa9ce48a9db9be487e.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201013/f43b5f27e4194b0ab3d593ecb7935fbd.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">格彩臂金龟。受访者供图</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201013/7db594dd1a504505af810011444969b4.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
